        "Description": "As a knight of the Royal Order,\r\nI must further my training, but\r\nmy fellow knights don\u0027t seem\r\nkeen on hunting with me. Again,\r\nforgive me for asking a personal\r\nfavor, but would you be willing\r\nto accompany me on this quest?",
